summary: A quiet little home in the woods of Falkreath with a dark secret.
descriptionHtml:
[img=center]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/40046631/wcsmall.jpg[/img]

[b]Description:[/b]
Ever wanted quiet little home near Falkreath? Well this is the mod for you. This mod adds a decent size home with everything you need to make a living out in the moody wilderness of Falkreath. Not only is this a home, a surprise is in store if you can find the secrets. Best way to find it is to travel to Falkreath and a not-so-friendly man will want teach you a lesson. Then loot his body.

This mod did take me awhile to make, please provide feedback about what you liked, any bugs, and suggestions  that you may have.


Location:
Go outside the inn in Falkreath. A man with the key to the cabin and a note for the directions to the cabin.


Workshop Link:
[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=68682494]Wanderer\\\\\\\'s Cabin[/url]


Notes:
-If you have Warzones, be careful.
-Use a realistic lighting mod to make the lightling look nice.


Versions:
v1.6
 -Completely got rid of saber cat version
 -Added the FaceGen data to this .RAR file
v1.5
 -Added more storage
 -Fixed seam in ceiling
 -Added some more weapon plaques
 -Added Sabre Cat (Only in optional version)
v1.0:
-Initial Release


*Note: I uploaded this originally on my old account, but I decided to re-upload and add a few things on this, my new account.
